# File: stylesheets/print.css.ab
# Purpose: Empty Compass print media stylesheet placeholder in the default stylesheets/ output directory
# Dependencies: []

## Overview
An empty CSS file at the default Compass `stylesheets/` output directory. Contains only the standard Compass print stylesheet welcome comment instructing how to import it for print media. No actual print-specific styles have been defined.

## Interface
No exports. Empty placeholder stylesheet.

## Dependencies
No project-level dependencies.

## Implementation Notes
- 4 lines — only the Compass welcome/import comment, no actual CSS rules
- Located in the default Compass output directory at the project root
- Counterpart to `app/styles/print.css` and `app/assets/css/print.css` — all three are empty
- The `stylesheets/` location is the Compass default; the project uses `app/assets/css/` as its primary output
